OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F415A1779714673
OL,3,CThree Kent villages enter third day
OL,4,Cwithout water amid 'historic'
OL,5,Ctemperatures
OL,7,FResidents of three villages in Kent
OL,8,Fare continuing to be without water for
OL,9,Fa third consecutive day as parts of
OL,10,Fthe UK swelter under ''historic'' May
OL,11,Ftemperatures.
OL,13,FSupply issues in Charing, Challock and
OL,14,FMolash were first reported at around
OL,15,F8:30am on Saturday morning.
OL,17,FSouth East Water (SEW) has apologised
OL,18,Ffor the problems, which it has blamed
OL,19,Fon a pumping station.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G1/5
