CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F415A1779714673
OL,3,CThree Kent villages enter third day
OL,4,Cwithout water amid 'historic'
OL,5,Ctemperatures
OL,7,FA bottled water station had been set
OL,8,Fup over the weekend for affected
OL,9,Fresidents. It reopened this morning at
OL,10,F8am.
OL,12,FIt comes as the UK saw its hottest May
OL,13,Fday for at least 79 years on Sunday.
OL,15,FSubscribe free to our weekly
OL,16,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,17,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,18,Finbox every Friday morning.
