PN,41503
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F415A1779714673
OL,3,CThree Kent villages enter third day
OL,4,Cwithout water amid 'historic'
OL,5,Ctemperatures
OL,7,FSEW had said the issue was resolved
OL,8,Fovernight on Saturday, but that supply
OL,9,Fproblems resurfaced the following
OL,10,Fmorning.
OL,12,FIn an update on Sunday evening, the
OL,13,Fwater supplier said: "We are sorry to
OL,14,Fcustomers in the Charing, Challock and
OL,15,FMolash areas who have been impacted by
OL,16,Fongoing water supply issues again
OL,17,Ftoday.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G3/5
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
