FL,416,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41504
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F415A1779714673
OL,3,CThree Kent villages enter third day
OL,4,Cwithout water amid 'historic'
OL,5,Ctemperatures
OL,7,F"With the increased demand for
OL,8,Fdrinking water in the hot weather,
OL,9,Fwe're currently struggling to pump
OL,10,Fwater to customers on higher ground at
OL,11,Fpeak times during the day.
OL,13,F"We're sorry to these customers for
OL,14,Fthe disruption this is causing. We
OL,15,Fknow water supply issues during hot
OL,16,Fweather are deeply frustrating and
OL,17,Fincredibly inconvenient.
OL,19,F"We're still working hard to restore
OL,20,Ftap water to all our customers as
OL,21,Fquickly as possible."
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G4/5
